# [yatt-pipe](https://github.com/yatt-ai/yatt-pipe) Mocha Examples

Examples for reporting Mocha test results with `yatt-pipe`. It supports both [usage as an NPM package](.github/workflows/installed-demo.yml) and [usage via GitHub action](.github/workflows/gh-actions-demo.yml).

## Installation

This project requires Node.js version 18 or higher.

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install
```

## Running Tests

```bash
# Run tests with Mocha
npm run mocha

# Run tests with Mocha and generate JUnit report
npm run mocha-junit
```

